-- Beckons Gains in Mumbai on Algae Technology Transfer Agreement With Jilani
-- Tuhin Kar
-- 2010-07-06T03:59:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-06/beckons-gains-in-mumbai-on-algae-technology-transfer-agreement-with-jilani.html

          
          
             Beckons Industries Ltd. gained as
much as 10.4 percent in Mumbai trading after saying it signed an
agreement with Hong Kong-based Jilani International for transfer
of algae technology to countries including China and Singapore.  
          
          


  


        